        "text": "IPTVnator is an open-source cross-platform IPTV player built with Electron and Angular; it supports M3U/M3U8 playlists, XMLTV EPG, radio playlists, Xtream Codes, Stalker portals, external players, favorites, recent items, and a Docker/self-hosted option, but does not provide playlists or digital content.",
        "truth": "source_verified",
        "intent": "intended",
